Package de.fraunhofer.iais.eis

Interface ParticipantCertificateRevokedMessage

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Message, ModelClass, NotificationMessage, ParticipantNotificationMessage
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ParticipantCertificateRevokedMessageImpl
    public interface ParticipantCertificateRevokedMessage
extends ParticipantNotificationMessage
    Indicates that a (previously certified) Participant is no more certified. This could happen, for instance, if the Certification Body revokes a granted certificate or if the certificate just expires.
